                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- leave house reviews -->
                <div class="leave_a_review">
                    <h2>0 Reviews</h2>
                    <form action="">
                        <small>Leave a review</small>
                        <textarea class="form-control" aria-label="With textarea" rows="6"></textarea>
                        <div class="votes">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-success mt-2" type="submit">1</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-success mt-2" type="submit">2</button>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-success mt-2" type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <!-- house reviews -->
                <div class="review mt-lg-4 p-3">
                    <!-- guest avatar -->
                    <div class="host_avatar mt-lg-2">
                        <div class="avatar_img circular--square" style="background-image: url('https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/11.jpg');">
                        </div>
                        <div class="avatar_img m-lg-2">
                            <small>19 Jan 2022</small>
                            <h6>Riccardo Ferrara</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- guest comment -->
                    <p>This place is fantastic! The views are breathtaking and the host is very nice. My family and I had an amazing experience.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="review mt-lg-4 p-3">
                    <!-- guest avatar -->
                    <div class="host_avatar mt-lg-2">
                        <div class="avatar_img circular--square" style="background-image: url('https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/11.jpg');">
                        </div>
                        <div class="avatar_img m-lg-2">
                            <small>19 Jan 2022</small>
                            <h6>Riccardo Ferrara</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- guest comment -->
                    <p>This place is fantastic! The views are breathtaking and the host is very nice. My family and I had an amazing experience.</p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- send message / book -->
            <div class="col">
                <div class="send_message">
                    <h3>$350/night</h3>
                    <small>0 Reviews</small>
                    <form action="">
                        <textarea class="form-control" aria-label="With textarea" placeholder="Send the host a message..." rows="5"></textarea>
                        <button class="btn btn-success mt-2" type="submit">Request Booking</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- end grid -->
        </div>
        <!-- end container -->
    </div>


</section>